{"tid":2488583,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳冠希與C女星一夜情 床上邀拍裸照被拒絕（白露眉）","createTime":"2021-04-14T10:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T10:48:13.000Z","uid":52978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"67d493c996696e18a86b473bf9dbad8439eaae87","tid":2488583,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"非常人●非常事｜陳冠希與C女星一夜情 床上邀拍裸照被拒絕（白露眉）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210414/HMCXSP6YOJA3JEAU524V7TJ4UQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210414%2FHMCXSP6YOJA3JEAU524V7TJ4UQ%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=a7a5a763\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210414%2FHMCXSP6YOJA3JEAU524V7TJ4UQ%2F&h=f801cb53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210414/HMCXSP6YOJA3JEAU524V7TJ4UQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已為人妻的C女星曾告訴我，她曾與Edison玩過一夜情，C女星表示：「嗰晚喺中環一間酒吧撞見Edison，初時我哋唔係好熟，但有一啲共同朋友，所以就一齊坐低玩。嗰晚大家飲到大大哋，Edison帶咗我返屋企，喺床上佢問我可唔可以影我嘅裸照，純粹留個紀念，我心諗點可以俾人影呢啲相？有乜鬼好留念，所以我話唔影得，仲要佢熄晒燈先可以有下文，嗱！呢樣嘢佢幾gentle，我話唔影佢冇逼我，叫佢熄燈，佢即刻熄，黑晒我覺得比較有安全感。」"},{"pid":"04940018bf73076284c990edc46221569e52aaab","tid":2488583,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"C女星，大家有冇頭緒？"},{"pid":"d1f09bbefafe1e49843d661df3ca3002e2101b69","tid":2488583,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae32e3a1f81b29f7a5f6854fb40bd27f582a318c","tid":2488583,"uid":4179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04940018bf73076284c990edc46221569e52aaab","tid":2488583,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"C女星，大家有冇頭緒？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:39:08.000Z","msg":"希哥食既女多過全部連登仔加埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\